Express%20Mumbai.%20He%20said%20that%20a%20parcel%20containing%20a%20passport%2C%20three%20ATM%20cards%2C%20one%20laptop%2C%20and%20150%20gm%20of%20MDMA%20was%20mailed%20in%20her%20name%20with%20her%20Aadhaar%20number%20to%20one%20John%20David%20in%20Cambodia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhen%20she%20said%20she%20knew%20nothing%20about%20the%20parcel%20in%20question%2C%20the%20person%20transferred%20the%20call%20to%20someone%2C%20who%20he%20said%2C%20was%20a%20police%20official%20from%20Andheri%20Mumbai%20police%20station%20to%20help%20her%20file%20an%20online%20complaint.%20The%20%E2%80%98cop%E2%80%99%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20asked%20her%20to%20share%20her%20Aadhar%20number%2C%20which%20she%20did%2C%20and%20was%20told%20that%20there%20were%2018%20more%20cases%20against%20her%20Aadhaar.%20She%20was%20told%20that%20she%20is%20among%20108%20suspects%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20and%20a%20human%20trafficking%20case.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20same%20day%2C%20she%20received%20a%20call%20from%20another%20official%20who%20said%20was%20from%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%20She%20was%20told%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98CBI%20official%E2%80%99%20specifically%20not%20to%20let%20her%20know%20anything%20about%20the%20supposed%20case%20and%20who%20she%20was%20talking%20to.%20If%20she%20did%2C%20even%20those%20person(s)%20would%20be%20implicated%20in%20the%20case%2C%20he%20warned.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20transfer%20Rs%2014.5%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBelow%20is%20the%20first-person%20account%20by%20the%20woman%2C%20which%20gives%20a%20blow-by-blow%20account%20of%20the%20alleged%20scam%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2018%2C%20at%20around%209%3A30%20am%2C%20I%20got%20a%20call%20on%20my%20mobile%20number.%20A%20man%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20from%20DHL%20Express%20Mumbai%20said%20that%20a%20parcel%20numbered%20AWB7089523554%20containing%20a%20passport%2C%20three%20ATM%20cards%2C%20one%20laptop%2C%20and%20150%20gm%20of%20MDMA%20(a%20contraband%20drug)%20was%20mailed%20in%20my%20name%20with%20my%20Aadhaar%20number%20to%20a%20John%20David%20in%20Cambodia%20180204%20(later%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20had%20got%20a%20call%20from%20a%20similar%20number%20the%20previous%20day%20as%20well%2C%20at%20around%20the%20same%20time%20of%20the%20day%2C%20which%20I%20did%20not%20receive).%20I%20told%20this%20person%20that%20I%20had%20not%20sent%20any%20such%20parcel.%20He%20then%20transferred%20my%20call%20to%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Andheri%2C%20Mumbai%20for%20an%20online%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20person%20who%20spoke%20at%20this%20number%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20constable%20with%20the%20Mumbai%20Police.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20was%20checking%20from%20some%20site%20whether%20any%20other%20case%20had%20been%20lodged%20against%20my%20Aadhaar.%20After%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20he%20said%20that%20there%20were%20eighteen%20more%20cases%20against%20my%20Aadhaar.%20I%20was%20one%20of%20the%20108%20people%20on%20the%20suspect%20list%20of%20a%20money%20laundering%20and%20human%20trafficking%20case%20where%20the%20main%20suspect%20was%20Sanjay.%20He%20added%20that%20in%20a%20testimony%20in%20court%2C%20Sanjay%20claimed%20that%20eighteen%20persons%20had%20testified%20to%20transferring%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%2038%20crore%20in%20an%20HDFC%20account%20in%20my%20name.%20According%20to%20Sanjay%2C%20these%20persons%20had%20transferred%20the%20money%20as%20per%20my%20instructions%2C%20and%20I%20had%20retained%2010%20percent%20of%20this%20amount%20in%20the%20HDFC%20account.%20When%20I%20told%20the%20person%20pretending%20to%20be%20a%20constable%20that%20I%20had%20no%20HDFC%20account%2C%20he%20said%20that%20my%20verbal%20statement%20would%20have%20no%20standing%20in%20the%20court%20and%20that%20I%20had%20to%20build%20a%20case%20to%20prove%20my%20innocence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20so-called%20police%20constable%20told%20me%20that%20many%20Indian%20citizens%20had%20been%20trafficked%20to%20Cambodia%2C%20of%20which%20about%20sixty%20were%20still%20there.%20They%20had%20been%20tortured%20and%20their%20various%20organs%20were%20removed%20(e.g.%2C%20kidney%20and%20eye).%20He%20asked%20whether%20I%20realised%20what%20these%20persons%20were%20going%20through%20and%20what%20I%20would%20do%20to%20help%20them.%20Not%20being%20able%20to%20think%20clearly%20because%20of%20the%20panic%20that%20I%20felt%20upon%20learning%20that%20I%20was%20embroiled%20in%20a%20legal%20case%20of%20such%20gravity%2C%20I%20said%20that%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know.%20He%20then%20asked%20what%20I%20would%20have%20done%20if%20any%20of%20the%20victims%20was%20a%20family%20member.%20To%20this%2C%20I%20said%20that%20I%20would%20have%20tried%20to%20save%20them.%20He%20said%20that%20my%20testimony%20was%20important%20in%20saving%20these%20people.%20He%20added%20that%20as%20this%20was%20a%20top-secret%20case%20of%20national%20security%2C%20I%20could%20not%20discuss%20it%20with%20anyone.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20one%20of%20the%20other%20suspects%20in%20the%20case%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20businessman%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20soon%20after%20he%20shared%20the%20details%20of%20this%20case%20with%20his%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20gave%20the%20phone%20to%20a%20person%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20CBI%20officer%2C%20and%20introduced%20himself%20as%20Ashok%20Yadav.%20At%2010%3A15%20am%2C%20I%20got%20a%20WhatsApp%20text%20from%20the%20number%20of%20the%20call%20which%20said%20%E2%80%9CMIDC%20recording%20No.%2072513%2F2023.%E2%80%9D%20The%20person%20pretending%20to%20be%20Ashok%20Yadav%20asked%20me%20to%20send%20a%20message%20containing%20my%20full%20name%20along%20with%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9CID%20theft.%E2%80%9D%20After%20I%20did%20so%2C%20he%20started%20a%20WhatsApp%20video%20call%20on%20the%20same%20number%2C%20in%20which%20he%20could%20see%20me%2C%20but%20I%20could%20only%20see%20the%20logo%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%2C%20which%20was%20the%20display%20picture%20of%20this%20WhatsApp%20account.%20Yadav%20told%20me%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20was%20alone%20in%20the%20house.%20So%2C%20when%20my%20house%20help%20came%20out%20from%20the%20kitchen%20into%20the%20room%20where%20I%20was%2C%20I%20signalled%20to%20her%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20Since%20she%20could%20not%20leave%20the%20house%20without%20entering%20the%20room%20where%20I%20was%2C%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20kitchen%20for%20about%20two%20hours%2C%20until%20the%20call%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Yadav%20told%20me%20that%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20was%20out%20against%20me.%20I%20had%20two%20options%3B%20either%20I%20could%20face%20imprisonment%20for%20ninety%20days%20and%20be%20questioned%20in%20custody%20or%20I%20could%20be%20subjected%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpriority%20investigation%E2%80%9D%20as%20I%20was%20a%20senior%20citizen%2C%20a%20woman%2C%20and%20a%20doctor%20(at%20some%20point%20I%20was%20asked%20what%20I%20did).%20During%20the%20priority%20investigation%2C%20I%20could%20not%20receive%20or%20make%20any%20calls%20or%20allow%20anyone%20in%20the%20house.%20All%20my%20assets%20will%20be%20examined%2C%20and%20if%20found%20to%20be%20legally%20acquired%2C%20the%20charges%20against%20me%20will%20be%20dropped.%20However%2C%20if%20any%20asset%20could%20not%20be%20accounted%20for%20legally%2C%20then%20all%20my%20assets%20would%20be%20frozen.%20If%20I%20did%20not%20comply%2C%20I%20would%20be%20arrested%2C%20interrogated%20in%20custody%2C%20and%20my%20assets%20would%20be%20frozen%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20around%2010%3A45%20am%2C%20Yadav%20asked%20me%20to%20send%20him%20a%20photograph%20of%20my%20Aadhaar%20(front%20and%20back)%20through%20WhatsApp.%20Soon%20after%20I%20did%20so%2C%20I%20got%20the%20soft%20copies%20of%20a%20series%20of%20documents%20on%20WhatsApp%20from%20the%20same%20number.%20All%20of%20them%20had%20the%20logo%20of%20the%20CBI%20or%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20and%20my%20name%20and%20Aadhaar%20number.%20The%20first%20document%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%9CConfidentiality%20Agreement%2C%E2%80%9D%20(image%201)%20was%20signed%20by%20a%20Special%20Director%3A%20Praveen%20Sood.%20The%20second%20document%20and%20third%20documents%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%9CAsset%20Seizure%20Order%E2%80%9D%20(image%202)%20and%20%E2%80%9CWarrant%20of%20Arrest%E2%80%9D%20(image%203)%20respectively%2C%20were%20signed%20by%20a%20Subhas%20Chandrashekhar%20Tayde%20(Metropolitan%20Magistrate%2C%20Andheri%2C%20Mumbai).%20Yadav%20asked%20me%20whether%20I%20had%20read%20and%20understood%20these%20documents.%20Since%20I%20was%20not%20in%20a%20state%20of%20mind%20to%20read%20these%20documents%20carefully%2C%20I%20just%20said%20yes.%20He%20explained%20that%20as%20per%20the%20first%20document%2C%20I%20have%20sworn%20to%20not%20share%20the%20details%20of%20this%20investigation%20with%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20Yadav%20asked%20me%20to%20give%20him%20the%20details%20of%20all%20my%20assets.%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20tell%20him%20the%20last%20four%20digits%20of%20all%20my%20bank%20accounts%2C%20the%20approximate%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20each%20account%2C%20and%20other%20details%20of%20my%20assets.%20He%20wanted%20to%20know%20for%20which%20accounts%20I%20did%20online%20banking%20and%20for%20which%20I%20went%20to%20the%20bank%20physically.%20Yadav%20asked%20me%20to%20log%20into%20the%20internet%20banking%20of%20one%20of%20my%20accounts%20and%20tell%20him%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20it.%20Given%20how%20scared%20I%20was%2C%20I%20twice%20made%20an%20error%20in%20entering%20the%20password%20but%20could%20log%20in%20successfully%20in%20the%20third%20attempt.%20When%20I%20checked%20and%20told%20him%20that%20there%20were%20Rs%208.25%20lakhs%20in%20this%20account%2C%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20transfer%20Rs%208%20lakh%20into%20a%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20account%20in%20the%20name%20of%20M%20P%20Furniture%20(account%20no%3A%209962002100004155%3B%20IFSC%3A%20PUNB0996200%20(current)%3B%20state%3A%20Uttar%20Pradesh).%20He%20asked%20me%20to%20keep%20the%20remaining%20Rs%2025%2C000%20for%20my%20expenses.%20Yadav%20said%20that%20since%20many%20bank%20officers%2C%20insurance%20agents%2C%20and%20police%20officers%20were%20involved%20in%20this%20international%20racket%2C%20my%20assets%20could%20not%20be%20scrutinised%20in%20my%20bank%20branches.%20So%2C%20I%20had%20to%20transfer%20my%20money%20to%20this%20%E2%80%9Csupervision%20account%E2%80%9D%20for%20scrutiny.%20Yadav%20asked%20me%20to%20use%20my%20mobile%20phone%20camera%20in%20the%20reversal%20mode%20and%20place%20it%20close%20to%20the%20laptop%20screen%20so%20that%20he%20could%20see%20if%20I%20made%20a%20mistake.%20I%20transferred%20the%20money%20at%20around%201%3A30%20pm%2C%20and%20around%202%3A15%20pm%2C%20I%20received%20a%20document%20titled%20%E2%80%9CNotarized%20Supervision%20Acknowledgment%E2%80%9D%20(image%204)%20on%20WhatsApp%20as%20a%20receipt%20of%20the%20transfer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F687691020%2FRedacted-Docs%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Redacted%20Docs%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3ERedacted%20Docs%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F286754081%2FThe-Wire%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20The%20Wire's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F687691020%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-Ui8qTFseXPCzMm1YW59a%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7085624509033779%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Redacted%20Docs%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20then%20asked%20me%20to%20go%20to%20the%20local%20bank%20branch%20of%20one%20of%20my%20other%20accounts%2C%20break%20a%20fixed%20deposit%20and%20transfer%20all%20but%20about%20Rs%2020%2C000%20from%20this%20account%20to%20the%20same%20so-called%20supervision%20account.%20By%20around%204%20pm%2C%20I%20had%20transferred%20Rs%206.5%20lakh%20from%20this%20account.%20Yadav%20asked%20me%20for%20the%20UTR%20number%20to%20confirm%20the%20transfer.%20When%20I%20sent%20him%20a%20photograph%20of%20a%20paper%20with%20this%20number%2C%20he%20insisted%20that%20I%20also%20get%20it%20stamped%20and%20signed%20by%20a%20bank%20employee.%20After%20I%20did%20as%20I%20was%20instructed%2C%20Yadav%20told%20me%20to%20wait%20in%20the%20branch%20until%20he%20confirmed%20the%20transfer.%20After%20some%20time%2C%20I%20was%20allowed%20to%20go%20home.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20got%20a%20receipt%20on%20WhatsApp%20for%20this%20transfer%20as%20well%20(image%205).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%2C%20who%20was%20supposed%20to%20come%20to%20Delhi%20from%20Ranchi%20by%20an%20evening%20flight%20called%20me%20several%20times%20during%20the%20day%2C%20but%20I%20did%20not%20receive%20her%20calls%2C%20as%20I%20was%20told%20repeatedly%20that%20whoever%20learns%20about%20the%20investigation%20will%20also%20become%20liable%20for%20imprisonment.%20Sensing%20that%20something%20was%20amiss%2C%20she%20messaged%20me%20asking%20why%20I%20was%20not%20picking%20up%20her%20calls%20and%20whether%20I%20was%20hurt.%20I%20kept%20replying%20that%20I%20could%20not%20tell%20her%20over%20the%20phone%20what%20was%20happening.%20She%20then%20began%20to%20ask%20some%20of%20my%20friends%20who%20live%20nearby%20to%20find%20out%20what%20was%20happening%20to%20me.%20One%20friend%20called%20while%20I%20was%20in%20the%20bank%2C%20but%20I%20did%20not%20receive%20her%20call.%20Another%20came%20home%20after%20I%20had%20returned%20from%20the%20bank%2C%20but%20initially%2C%20I%20did%20not%20let%20her%20in%2C%20as%20I%20was%20told%20that%20I%20had%20to%20be%20alone%20during%20the%20investigation.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20opened%20the%20door%20for%20her%20but%20went%20to%20another%20room%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20scamster%20when%20he%20called.%20She%20forced%20me%20to%20eat%20something%2C%20as%20I%20had%20not%20eaten%20since%20morning%20and%20then%20took%20me%20to%20her%20house%20where%20I%20stayed%20until%20my%20daughter%20came.%20I%20did%20not%20tell%20her%20anything%2C%20as%20I%20could%20not%20risk%20her%20going%20to%20prison%20because%20of%20learning%20about%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20told%20me%20to%20update%20him%20about%20my%20whereabouts%20and%20activity%20every%20half%20an%20hour.%20Apart%20from%20information%20about%20my%20assets%2C%20he%20also%20asked%20me%20about%20my%20daughter%3B%20her%20name%2C%20phone%20number%2C%20what%20she%20does%2C%20whether%20she%20is%20married%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20I%20last%20updated%20him%20on%20WhatsApp%20at%20around%2010%3A30%20pm.%20At%20around%20midnight%2C%20when%20my%20daughter%20and%20her%20partner%20reached%20home%2C%20and%20I%20narrated%20to%20them%20at%20length%20what%20had%20happened%20that%2C%20we%20figured%20that%20I%20had%20been%20scammed.%20I%20was%20flooded%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20relief%20as%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20was%20not%20in%20any%20danger%20of%20getting%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20from%20around%207%3A45%20am%20onwards%2C%20I%20got%20repeated%20messages%20for%20an%20update.%20At%20around%209%3A30%20am%2C%20I%20got%20a%20message%20that%20the%20court%20had%20issued%20an%20emergency%20notice%20in%20my%20name.%20Soon%20afterward%2C%20I%20blocked%20this%20number.%20We%20lodged%20an%20online%20complaint%20on%20the%20National%20Cyber%20Crime%20Portal%20at%20about%2011%3A30%20am%20and%20then%20went%20to%20the%20local%20cybercrime%20cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%20After%20much%20insistence%2C%20I%20got%20a%20signed%20acknowledgement%20of%20my%20complaint.%20Since%20then%2C%20we%20have%20made%20repeated%20trips%20to%20this%20cell%2C%20and%20also%20our%20local%20thana%2C%20but%20an%20FIR%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20scamsters%20have%20much%20of%20my%20private%20information%2C%20I%20have%20had%20to%20take%20a%20number%20of%20steps%20to%20reduce%20the%20possibility%20of%20getting%20scammed%20of%20more%20money.%20First%2C%20we%20got%20all%20my%20bank%20accounts%20blocked.%20Then%2C%20I%20got%20a%20new%20phone%20number%20and%20got%20it%20linked%20in%20place%20of%20my%20old%20number%20with%20these%20accounts.%20I%20have%20also%20ensured%20that%20my%20Aadhaar%20is%20delinked%20from%20all%20these%20accounts%2C%20to%20pre-empt%20the%20possibility%20of%20fraudulent%20Aadhaar-enabled%20transactions%20from%20any%20of%20these%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20recall%20the%20process%20by%20which%20I%20was%20scammed%2C%20several%20loopholes%20emerged%20in%20the%20story%20that%20I%20was%20told%20by%20the%20persons%20impostering%20as%20the%20police%20constable%20and%20the%20CBI%20officer.%20Taking%20advantage%20of%20my%20limited%20knowledge%20of%20the%20law%2C%20the%20scamsters%20could%20convince%20me%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20my%20arrest%20and%20seizure%20of%20my%20assets.%20Because%20of%20the%20immense%20fear%20that%20this%20created%20in%20me%2C%20I%20did%20as%20I%20was%20instructed.%20Further%2C%20I%20could%20not%20consult%20anyone%20as%20I%20was%20repeatedly%20told%20that%20whoever%20learns%20about%20this%20incident%2C%20will%20also%20become%20liable%20for%20imprisonment.%20Despite%20the%20ordeal%20that%20I%20was%20going%20through%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20the%20politeness%20of%20the%20CBI%20officer%2C%20and%20his%20apparent%20helpfulness%2C%20as%20he%20patiently%20guided%20me%20on%20whatever%20I%20needed%20to%20do.%20When%20my%20daughter%20first%20suggested%20that%20what%20happened%20that%20day%20may%20have%20been%20a%20scam%2C%20I%20dismissed%20the%20possibility%2C%20as%20I%20had%20even%20got%20supposed%20receipts%20for%20the%20transfers%2C%20which%20looked%20rather%20authentic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20nightmare%20is%20over%2C%20I%20am%20still%20very%20shaken.%20Amongst%20the%20various%20people%20to%20whom%20I%20have%20narrated%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20few%20%E2%80%93%20including%20a%20bank%20manager%2C%20a%20police%20officer%2C%20and%20some%20friends%20%E2%80%93%20have%20asked%20how%20I%20could%20trust%20unknown%20persons%20and%20transfer%20such%20large%20sums%20of%20money.%20Such%20persons%20fail%20to%20understand%20the%20extent%20of%20fear%20that%20the%20scamsters%20succeeded%20in%20creating%20in%20me.%20They%20are%2C%20after%20all%2C%20professionals%20in%20their%20field%2C%20just%20like%20I%20am%20in%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701169256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F28173221%2Fhacker-5471975_1280.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fimpersonation-threat-calls-a-first-person-account-by-a-woman-who-lost-rs-14-5-lakh-in-online-fraud%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2065-year-old%20doctor%20from%20Delhi%2C%20who%20was%20threatened%20to%20share%20her%20Aadhar%20number%20by%20fraudsters%2C%20was%20told%20she%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20'top-secret%20case%20of%20national%20security'%2C%20which%20she%20knew%20nothing%20of.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fimpersonation-threat-calls-a-first-person-account-by-a-woman-who-lost-rs-14-5-lakh-in-online-fraud%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Shin%20Ye%20replace%20Jeon%20So%20in%20%E2%80%98Running%20Man%E2%80%99%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701169219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105562871%2Cimgsize-475687.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fwill-shin-ye-eun-replace-jeon-so-mins-spot-in-running-man%2Farticleshow%2F105562899.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3