%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-silicon-valley-openai-sam-altman-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESatya%20Nadella%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20at%20the%20time.%20When%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20overturned%20Roe%20v.%20Wade%20last%20year%2C%20Kathleen%20Hogan%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20people%20officer%2C%20sent%20a%20companywide%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eemail%2C%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20difficult%20day%20for%20many%20of%20us%2C%20including%20me.%26quot%3B%20After%20Hamas%20attacked%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20the%20company%20issued%20several%20statements%20of%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20offered%20to%20match%20employee%20donations%20to%20Israeli%20organizations%2C%20including%20the%20nonprofit%20Friends%20of%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%2C%20and%20granted%20Microsoft's%203%2C000%20Israeli%20employees%20a%20%243%2C000%20stipend%20for%20%26quot%3Bunexpected%20expenses%20because%20of%20the%20situation.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20debate%20raging%20on%20Microsoft's%20internal%20message%20board%20is%20testing%20that%20new%20openness%20to%20mixing%20business%20and%20politics%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20it%20has%20at%20elite%20institutions%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-harvard-letter-students-hamas-israel-wall-street-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Columbia%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20Wall%20Street.%20Internal%20Microsoft%20posts%20and%20emails%20reviewed%20by%20BI%20offer%20a%20window%20into%20the%20anger%20and%20vitriol%20that%20workplaces%20across%20America%20grapple%20with%20as%20the%20war%20escalates.%20What%20was%20once%20the%20province%20of%20the%20watercooler%20has%20migrated%20to%20company-sponsored%20forums%20such%20as%20Slack%20and%20Viva%20Engage%2C%20forcing%20employers%20to%20decide%20where%20to%20draw%20the%20line%20on%20discussing%20politics%20at%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20actively%20attempted%20to%20regulate%20the%20internal%20debate%20over%20the%20war.%20It%20has%20advised%20managers%20to%20%26quot%3Bavoid%20providing%20additional%20commentary%20on%20the%20war%26quot%3B%20beyond%20the%20company's%20official%20statements.%20It%20has%20cut%20off%20the%20comments%20to%20Viva%20Engage%20posts%20it%20considered%20too%20incendiary.%20And%20in%20at%20least%20one%20instance%2C%20a%20manager%20has%20reprimanded%20an%20employee%20for%20a%20post%20deemed%20inappropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20internally%2C%20Microsoft's%20moves%20have%20only%20served%20to%20further%20inflame%20tensions.%20Some%20employees%20accuse%20the%20company%20of%20moderating%20posts%20that%20expressed%20concern%20for%20Palestinians%2C%20while%20its%20executives%20have%20openly%20expressed%20support%20for%20Israel.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20found%20particularly%20troubling%20is%20the%20double%20standard%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20reprimanded%20employee%2C%20who%20was%20ordered%20to%20stop%20posting%20political%20messages%20on%20Viva%20Engage%20after%20they%20shared%20news%20reports%20about%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20Gaza.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20our%20leaders%20do%20talk%20about%20politics%20at%20work%20very%20regularly%20%E2%80%94%20as%20I%20believe%20they%20should.%20This%20is%20the%20most%20taboo%20topic%20I've%20ever%20seen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20employees%20echoed%20that%20concern.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20very%20disappointing%20about%20Microsoft%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3Bis%20we%20chose%20this%20company%20because%20of%20its%20values%20and%20mission%20statement%20to%20'empower%20every%20person%20and%20every%20organization%20on%20the%20planet%20to%20achieve%20more.'%20Our%20mission%20statement%20says%20'every%20person%2C'%20but%20it%20feels%20like%20Palestinian%20employees%20don't%20exist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20insists%20that%20its%20role%20in%20the%20debate%20has%20been%20even-handed.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20explicit%20that%20our%20priority%20lies%20with%20our%20employees%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20taking%20a%20'side.'%26quot%3B%20But%20some%20employees%20who%20support%20Israel%20seem%20to%20believe%20the%20company%20shares%20their%20views%20on%20the%20war%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20feel%20emboldened%20to%20express%20hostility%20to%20coworkers%20they%20deem%20insufficiently%20pro-Israel%2C%20without%20fear%20of%20reprisal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHopefully%20you%20know%20that%20the%20entire%20company%20is%20reading%20your%20comments%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20posted%20in%20response%20to%20a%20discussion%20about%20ways%20to%20provide%20support%20to%20Palestinian%20civilians%20affected%20by%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20hopefully%20those%20employees%20will%20find%20themselves%20out%20of%20this%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20employee%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EComplicating%20Microsoft's%20role%20in%20the%20debate%20is%20the%20company's%20financial%20stake%20in%20Israel%2C%20where%20it%20has%20maintained%20offices%20since%201989.%20In%201991%2C%20the%20company%20opened%20its%20first%20research-and-development%20center%20outside%20the%20US%C2%A0in%20Haifa%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20first%20major%20tech%20companies%20to%20do%20so%20in%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20touts.%20Today%2C%20it%20has%20campuses%20in%20Herzliya%2C%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20Haifa%2C%20and%20Nazareth.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20it%20would%20invest%20up%20to%20%241.5%20billion%20to%20build%20a%20data%20center%20in%20Israel%20and%20expand%20its%20R%26amp%3BD%20for%20chips.%20Israel%2C%20Nadella%20told%20Prime%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetanyahu-cares-about-his-survival-more-than-gaza-idf-general-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBenjamin%20Netanyahu%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20very%20important%20development%20center%20for%20Microsoft.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20companies%2C%20Microsoft%20and%20its%20executives%20were%20quick%20to%20express%20its%20support%20for%20Israel%20after%20Hamas%20unleashed%20its%20assault%20on%20October%207%20and%20took%20some%20240%20hostages.%20%26quot%3BOur%20hearts%20are%20with%20all%20of%20you%20as%20we%20witness%20the%20devastating%20attack%20on%20your%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Charlie%20Bell%2C%20the%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20Microsoft%20security%2C%20emailed%20the%20company's%20Israeli%20employees%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20attack.%20%26quot%3BYour%20safety%20is%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20all%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20stand%20with%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20Guthrie%2C%20the%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20Microsoft%20cloud%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20internal%20email%20to%20the%20cloud%20and%20artificial-intelligence%20team%20on%20October%209.%20%26quot%3BMy%20thoughts%20are%20with%20our%20Israeli%20and%20Jewish%20colleagues%20and%20everyone%20impacted%20by%20these%20events%2C%20along%20with%20their%20friends%20and%20family%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajesh%20Jha%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20experiences%20and%20devices%20team%2C%20wrote%20on%20Viva%20Engage%20on%20October%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJha's%20post%20sparked%20an%20immediate%20response%20on%20the%20message%20board.%20%26quot%3BCan%20we%20also%20offer%20thoughts%2C%20prayers%20and%20blessings%20to%20any%20and%20all%20of%20our%20Palestinian%20colleagues%20who%20may%20be%20afraid%20for%20their%20families%20and%20friends%20and%20in%20fear%20for%20themselves%3F%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThis%20conflict%20has%20two%20sides%20of%20humans%20who%20are%20impacted%20by%20the%20violence%20of%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20response%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20infuriated%20another%20employee.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20saddening%20to%20see%20terror%20supporters%20among%20my%20colleagues%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWhoever%20suggests%20this%20massacre%20is%20part%20of%20some%20freedom%20fighting%20has%20lost%20all%20humanity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Israel%20launched%20a%20counteroffensive%20on%20Gaza%2C%20fierce%20arguments%20began%20to%20erupt%20on%20Viva%20Engage.%20%26quot%3BRest%20assured%20the%20IDF%20is%20doing%20all%20it%20can%20to%20avoid%20civilian%20casualties%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20posted%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20the%20people%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fgaza%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20elected%20Hamas%2C%20supported%20them%20and%20brought%20this%20on%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20can%20you%20put%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20the%20same%20category%20as%20terrorist%20organizations%3F%26quot%3B%20another%20employee%20responded.%20%26quot%3BKilling%20innocent%20civilians%20from%20either%20side%20is%20never%20right%2C%20and%20feeling%20bad%20for%20everyone%20involved%20is%20just%20basic%20human%20decency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20and%20we%20are%20fighting%20to%20liberate%20Israelis%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20from%20these%20terrorists%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20original%20poster%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BTrying%20to%20create%20a%20symmetry%20or%20depict%20it%20as%20a%20conflict%20with%202%20legitimate%20sides%20is%20either%20ignorant%20or%20immoral.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20post%2C%20one%20employee%20shared%20a%20message%20of%20concern%20for%20Microsoft%20employees%20who%20%26quot%3Bhave%20friends%20and%20family%20in%20Palestine%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThose%20people%20are%20currently%20being%20wiped%20and%20having%20their%20livelihoods%20destroyed.%20They%20are%20forbidden%20from%20food%2C%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20and%20basic%20medical%20supplies.%20They%20are%20not%20terrorists%20nor%20do%20they%20have%20an%20agenda%20against%20Israelis.%20Please%20stand%20on%20the%20same%20distance%20between%20both%20parties.%20That's%20the%20least%20you%20could%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20talking%20about%20terrorism%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20employee%20responded.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20justification%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20employee%20further%20fanned%20the%20flames%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20able%20to%20contain%20the%20evil%20inflicted%20on%20us%20on%20Saturday%20morning.%20That%20requires%20us%20to%20change%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20game.%20The%20Hamas%20infra%20in%20Gaza%20will%20be%20exterminated.%20The%20price%20on%20human%20life%20will%20be%20high%20since%20the%20cowards%20are%20hiding%20behind%20civilians.%E2%80%A6%20This%20is%20a%20survival%20war%20for%20Israel.%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20we%20will%20win%20this%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20infighting%20escalated%2C%20employees%20pressed%20the%20company%20to%20moderate%20the%20war%20of%20words.%20%26quot%3BMicrosoft%20Leadership%20needs%20to%20get%20a%20very%20strong%20grip%20on%20the%20messaging%20around%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20posted.%20%26quot%3BThey%20risk%20causing%20significant%20distress%20to%20many%20Palestinian%2C%20Arab%2C%20and%20Jewish%20employees%20when%20statements%20are%20crafted%20hastily%20and%20comment%20sections%20are%20left%20unmoderated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPalestinian%20people%20like%20me%20received%20zero%20support%20from%20our%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20employee%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20very%20clearly%20biased%20and%20our%20colleagues%20in%20Israel%20acted%20racist%20and%20rude%20and%20didn't%20acknowledge%20or%20respect%20our%20pain.%20Let%20us%20all%20align%20and%20respect%20'One%20Microsoft'%20to%20support%20one%20another.%20In%20such%20painful%20times%20there%20is%20opportunity%20to%20acknowledge%20some%20wrong%20behaviors%20that%20don't%20align%20with%20Microsoft%20values%20and%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20employee%20disagreed.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20that%20encourage%20terror%20acts%20and%20war%20crimes%20should%20get%20zero%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20posted.%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20has%20the%20right%20to%20defend%20itself.%20The%20only%20bias%20I%20see%20here%20is%20yours%2C%20where%20you%20don't%20see%20Hamas%20responsible%20for%20what%20is%20happening%20right%20now%20in%20the%20Gaza%20strip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20the%20company%20did%20step%20into%20the%20debate%2C%20%3Cspan%3Eit%20closed%20to%20comments%20many%20posts%20that%20expressed%20support%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine%20and%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20In%20mid-October%2C%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-shut-down-employee-chat-israel-hamas-war-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemployee%20posted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20felt%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20sense%20of%20disillusionment%20with%20our%20work%20and%20the%20company%26quot%3B%20over%20what%20they%20viewed%20as%20%26quot%3Bone-sided%20statements%26quot%3B%20by%20Microsoft's%20senior%20leaders.%20%26quot%3BIt%20saddens%20me%20to%20witness%20a%20company%20that%20so%20strongly%20promotes%20Diversity%20and%20Inclusion%20show%20such%20strong%20discrimination%20and%20marginalization%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20to%20me%20that%20the%20company%20is%20oblivious%20to%20the%20overwhelming%20and%20disproportionate%20suffering%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20closed%20the%20post%20to%20comments%20after%20600%20reactions%20and%2060%20comments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20closed%20several%20other%20posts%20to%20comments.%20One%20read%2C%20simply%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20demand%20a%20%23CeasefireNow%20Microsoft!!%26quot%3B%20Another%20was%20addressed%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bover%2010%2C000%20men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%20in%20Gaza%20who%20have%20been%20needlessly%20kil