ajor%20donors%20enraged%20by%20student%20statements%20they%20view%20as%20anti-Israel.%20Davis%20Polk%20%26amp%3B%20Wardwell%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20law%20firms%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3-harvard-columbia-law-students-lost-job-offers-israel-statements-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erescinded%20job%20offers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20students%20from%20Ivy%20League%20schools%20who%20criticized%20Israel's%20role%20in%20the%20conflict.%20Google%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%2C%20%26quot%3Bhas%20sunk%20into%20a%20morass%20of%20hostility%20and%20intolerance%26quot%3B%20for%20both%20Muslim%20and%20Jewish%20employees.%20And%20Apple%2C%20BI%20has%20learned%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-paused-jewish-and-muslim-employee-message-boards-messages-show-2023-11%23%3A~%3Atext%3DApple%2520paused%2520dedicated%2520internal%2520Slack%2CMicrosoft%2520also%2520did%2520so%2520recently.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindefinitely%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20Slack%20channels%20for%20Jewish%20and%20Muslim%20employees.%20(The%20company%20has%202%2C000%20employees%20in%20Israel%2C%20where%20it%20maintains%20an%20R%26amp%3BD%20center%20north%20of%20Tel%20Aviv.)%20%26quot%3BWe're%20taking%20this%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Apple%20employee%20responsible%20for%20the%20Muslim%20Slack%20channel%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20a%20respectful%20environment%20for%20our%20communities%20during%20a%20painful%20and%20tragic%20time.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Microsoft%2C%20the%20attempt%20to%20moderate%20the%20internal%20debate%20finally%20made%20it%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20top.%20On%20November%208%2C%20after%20more%20than%201%2C000%20employees%20signed%20a%20letter%20on%20Viva%20Engage%20urging%20the%20company%20to%20support%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhamas-releases-17-hostages-israel-cease-fire-agreement-2023-1