0annual%20report%20on%20worker%20safety%20in%20the%20Indian%20auto%20sector%20found%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20women%20workers%20are%20forced%20to%20operate%20under%20duress%2C%20either%20by%20their%20employer%2C%20contractor%20or%20other%20circumstances%2C%20and%20without%20adequate%20training%20or%20safety%20equipment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20workers%20in%20Faridabad%2C%20Haryana%20outlined%20these%20problems%20in%20the%20auto%20industry%2C%20listing%20the%20high%20risk%20of%20injury%2C%20high%20production%20pressure%2C%20failure%20to%20be%20provided%20with%20ESIC%20cards%20and%20lower%20salaries%20than%20their%20male%20counterparts%20in%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20auto%20sector%20brands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20these%20hardships%2C%20working%20is%20a%20necessity%20for%20thousands%20of%20women%20like%20us%20so%20that%20we%20can%20provide%20good%20education%20and%20upbringing%20to%20our%20children%2C%20and%20also%2C%20our%20safety%20should%20be%20prioritised%20to%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20injuries.%20We%20request%20you%20understand%20our%20problems%20and%20ensure%20at%20least%20equal%20working%20conditions%20for%20women%20as%20for%20men%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20one%20of%20several%20accounts%20highlighted%20in%20the%205th%20annual%20%E2%80%98CRUSHED%E2%80%99%20report%20by%20the%20Safe%20In%20India%20Foundation%20(SII)%2C%20which%20had%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20the%20injuries%20faced%20by%20women%20workers%2C%20including%20first-hand%20accounts%20of%20women%20across%20several%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Threatened%20with%20firing%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20September%2023%2C%20SII%20conducted%20a%20focused%20group%20discussion%20with%2022%20injured%20women%20workers%20operating%20power%20press%20machines%20in%20Faridabad.%20These%20accounts%20expressed%20that%20in%20some%20factories%2C%20women%20make%20up%20the%20majority%20of%20machine%20operators%2C%20but%20that%20the%20consequences%20of%20being%20injured%20for%20women%20are%20much%20higher%20than%20for%20men.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20women%20find%20themselves%20without%20jobs%20after%20getting%20injured%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSeveral%20who%20have%20been%20given%20jobs%20are%20threatened%20with%20firing%20if%20they%20advocate%20new%20methods%20to%20prevent%20accidents%20or%20ask%20for%20documentation%20to%20get%20pensions%20and%20other%20funds%20due%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20auto%20sector%20contributes%20to%207.1%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20GDP%20and%20employs%20about%203.7%20million%20people.%20SII%20stated%20that%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%20alone%2C%20thousands%20of%20crushing%20injuries%20to%20workers%2C%20both%20men%20and%20women%2C%20continue%20to%20occur%20in%20the%20auto%20sector%20supply%20chain%20each%20year.%20Further%2C%20almost%20a%20quarter%20of%20crushing%20injuries%20on%20machines%20happen%20to%20unskilled%20helpers%2C%20who%2C%20legally%2C%20should%20not%20be%20operating%20these%20machines%20that%20require%20skilled%20operators.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20crush%20injuries%20continue%20to%20result%20in%20an%20average%20of%20two%20fingers%20lost%20per%20injured%20worker%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Improve%20laws%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWorkers%20facing%20injuries%20and%20losing%20fingers%20is%20a%20problem%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20of%20all%20the%20top%2010%20large%20auto%20sector%20brands%2C%20including%20Maruti-Suzuki%2C%20Honda%20and%20TATA%2C%20according%20to%20SII%E2%80%99s%20report.%20SII%20said%20these%20accidents%20have%20been%20underreported%20for%20decades%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20that%20there%20has%20not%20been%20data%20released%20since%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202020%2C%20%E2%80%98CRUSHED%E2%80%99%20found%20more%20than%201%2C000%20workers%20to%20face%20injuries%20in%20Haryana.%20The%20Haryana%20state-reported%20number%20was%20only%2068.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnless%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20industry%20itself%20improves%20the%20process%20of%20collecting%20and%20reporting%20accurate%20information%20on%20such%20accidents%20and%20injuries%2C%20introduces%20more%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20the%20relevant%20departments%20and%20agencies%2C%20any%20regional%2Fnational%20efforts%20to%20prevent%20these%20injuries%20and%20improve%20Indian%20manufacturing%20will%20not%20be%20as%20effective%20as%20they%20can%20and%20should%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20SII%E2%80%99s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20SII%20urged%20for%20more%20effective%20government%20intervention%20and%20more%20focus%20on%20Occupational%20Safety%20and%20Health%20(OSH)%20labour%20codes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20urge%20the%20appropriate%20governments%20to%20incorporate%20the%20reported%20suggestions%20while%20setting%20up%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Ecommittees%20and%20formalising%20labour%20codes.%20Only%20then%2C%20we%20can%20achieve%20%E2%80%98Sabka%20Saath%20Sabka%20Vikas%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Make%20in%20India%20responsibly%2C%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701167435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F28142122%2F49700185348_8e3b03a531_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwomen-in-the-auto-sector-among-thousands-losing-fingers-in-workplace-injuries-annually-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Safe%20In%20India%20Foundation