report-123112800603_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%2041%20Workers%20Got%20Trapped%20Inside%20Uttarakhand%20Tunnel%20For%2017%20Days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%2041%20workers%20trapped%20in%20an%20Uttarakhand%20tunnel%20for%2017%20days%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20rescued%20anytime%20now%2C%20as%20the%20manual%20drilling%20team%20clearing%20the%20debris%20that%20blocks%20their%20escape%20is%20metres%20away%20from%20reaching%20them.%20The%20operation%2C%20which%20faced%20several%20setbacks%20owing%20to%20the%20difficult%20terrain%2C%20is%20now%20on%20the%20threshold%20of%20success.%20As%20the%20country%20has%20its%20fingers%20crossed%20and%20hands%20joined%20in%20prayer%2C%20here's%20a%20look%20at%20how%20the%20workers%20got%20stuck%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Tunnel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%204.5%20km-tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Centre's%20ambitious%20Char%20Dham%20project%20aimed%20at%20providing%20all-weather%20connectivity%20between%20four%20prominent%20Hindu%20shrines%20in%20Uttarakhand%20-%20Badrinath%2C%20Kedarnath%2C%20Gangotri%20and%20Yamunotri.%20Also%20known%20as%20Silkyara%20tunnel%2C%20this%20tunnel%20is%20on%20the%20route%20connecting%20Silkyara%20and%20Dandalgaon%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-uttarkashi-tunnel-rescue-operation-live-updates-few-metres-of-digging-left-big-breakthrough-expected-today-4613105%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUttarkashi%20district%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20a%20double-lane%20tunnel%20and%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20under%20Char%20Dham%20project.%20About%202.4%20km%20of%20the%20under-construction%20tunnel%20from%20the%20Silkyara%20side%20and%201.75%20km%20from%20the%20other%20side%20has%20been%20built.%20The%20tunnel%2C%20once%20complete%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20cut%20down%20travel%20time%20by%20an%20hour.%20The%20project%20to%20build%20the%20tunnel%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20by%20Hyderabad-based%20Navayuga%20Engineering%20Company%20Limited%2C%20which%20has%20reportedly%20handled%20such%20projects%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Went%20Wrong%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2012%2C%20a%20section%20of%20tunnel%20between%20205%20and%20260%20metres%20from%20the%20Silkyara%20side%20collapsed.%20Workers%20who%20were%20beyond%20the%20260-metre%20mark%20were%20trapped%2C%20with%20their%20exit%20blocked.%20Fortunately%20for%20them%2C%20the%20part%20of%20the%20tunnel%20where%20they%20are%20stuck%20has%20power%20and%20water%20supply.%20While%20government%20authorities%20have%20maintained%20that%20a%20detailed%20probe%20will%20reveal%20what%20led%20to%20the%20collapse%2C%20multiple%20theories%20are%20floating%20around.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20that%20a%20landslide%20in%20the%20fragile%20Himalayan%20region%20led%20to%20the%20collapse.%20Several%20experts%20have%20pointed%20out%20how%20hasty%20development%20in%20the%20ecologically%20sensitive%20region%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20Lapses%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20claims%20that%20the%20collapse%20was%20triggered%20by%20a%20blast%20carried%20out%20by%20construction%20teams%20building%20the%20tunnel.%20SP%20Sati%2C%20a%20geologist%20and%20professor%20of%20environmental%20science%20at%20Uttarakhand%20University%20of%20Horticulture%20and%20Forestry%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20agency%20will%20never%20accept%20this%2C%20but%20I%20am%20certain%20that%20a%20major%20blast%20led%20to%20this%20collapse.%26quot%3B%20NDTV%20had%20earlier%20reported%20that%20the%20construction%20plan%20for%20the%20tunnel%20mentioned%20an%20escape%20tunnel%2C%20but%20it%20was%20never%20built.%20International%20expert%20Arnold%20Dix%2C%20who%20has%20been%20at%20the%20site%2C%20was%20asked%20if%20the%20absence%20of%20an%20escape%20tunnel%20contributed%20to%20the%20situation.%20He%20said%20that%20globally%2C%20escape%20tunnels%20are%20put%20at%20the%20end%20%26quo