bat%20during%20a%20domestic%20match.%20As%20Azam%20Khan's%20team%20Karachi%20Whites%20took%20on%20Lahore%20Blues%20at%20the%20National%20Stadium%20on%20Sunday%2C%20his%20bat%20featured%20a%20Palestine%20flag.%20Subsequently%2C%20a%2050%25%20fine%20on%20the%20match%20fee%20was%20imposed%20on%20Azam.%20However%2C%20the%20PCB%20later%20reviewed%20and%20matter%20and%20decided%20to%20waive%20the%20penalty%20that%20was%20imposed%20by%20the%20match%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20release%2C%20the%20PCB%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAzam%20Khan's%2050%20per%20cent%20fine%20imposed%20by%20match%20officials%20has%20been%20reviewed%20and%20waived%20off%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karachi%20Whites%20wicketkeeper-batter%20was%20fined%2050%20percent%20of%20his%20match%20fee%20for%20being%20found%20guilty%20of%20committing%20a%20level-I%20offence%20during%20his%20side's%20National%20T20%20Cup%202023-24%20match%20against%20Lahore%20Blues%20at%20National%20Bank%20Stadium%2C%20Karachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzam%20was%20found%20to%20have%20violated%20Article%202.4%20of%20the%20PCB%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20For%20Players%20and%20Players%20Support%20Personnel%20for%20repeated%20failure%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20instruction%20or%20directive%20of%20an%20Umpire%20during%20a%20Match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayers%20and%20team%20officials%20are%20not%20permitted%20to%20wear%2C%20display%20or%20otherwise%20convey%20personal%20messages%20on%20their%20equipment%20unless%20approved%20in%20advance%20by%20both%20player%20or%20team%20official's%20cricket%20association%20and%20PCB%20Cricket%20Operations%20Department.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ICC%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20%26quot%3Bplayers%20shall%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20display%20messages%20that%20carry%20political%2C%20religious%2C%20or%20racial%20activities%20or%20causes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20young%20batter%20was%20fined%2050%25%20of%20his%20match%20fees.%20The%20batter%20was%20earlier%20warned%20by%20the%20referee%20not%20to%20display%20the%20unapproved%20logo%20(Palestine's%20flag)%20on%20his%20bat%20as%20it%20would%20be%20a%20breach%20of%20the%20ICC%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20is%20also%20a%20signatory%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20board%20told%20Geo%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20reported%20that%20Azam%20had%20used%20the%20same%20sticker%20in%20the%20last%20two%20matches%2C%20but%20was%20not%20informed%20or%20warned%20by%20the%20officials%20prior%20to%20Sunday's%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fine%20led%20to%20a%20furore%20on%20social%20media%20with%20cricket%20fans%20and%20people%20criticising%20the%20Board%20for%20imposing%20the%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20match%20in%20which%20Azam%20was%20fined%20was%20televised%20live.%20He%20was%20playing%20for%20the%20Karachi%20Whites%20against%20Lahore%20Blues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzam%20has%20not%20played%20for%20the%20national%20team%20since%202021%20but%20is%20a%20well-known%20figure%20in%20Pakistan%20cricket%20circles%20due%20to%20his%20big-hitting%20abilities%20in%20the%20T20%20format%20and%20is%20also%20a%20regular%20on%20the%20franchise%20cricket%20circuits%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20recent%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%2C%20Pakistan's%20wicketkeeper-batter%20Muhammad%20Rizwan%20had%20also%20tweeted%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Palestine%20people%20in%20Gaza%20but%20escaped%20any%20fine%20from%20the%20ICC%20which%20said%20it%20was%20his%20personal%20opinion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701166440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fk97d0tf_azam-khan_625x300_28_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-batter-fined-for-palestine-flag-on-bat-has-penalty-waived-off-by-pcb-4613