he%20best%20one%20available%20in%20Terminal%204%2C%20in%20my%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20boarded%20the%20aircraft%20about%2045%20minutes%20before%20departure%20and%20made%20our%20way%20to%20a%20pair%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20plane.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222975%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20blue%20pair%20of%20seats%20on%20Hawaiian.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564f3d3fd6200867dcfd7ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222495%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20seats%20onboard%20Hawaiian's%20Airbus%20A330.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHawaiian%20uses%20the%20widebody%20Airbus%20A330%20on%20its%20long-haul%20routes%20between%20Honolulu%20and%20the%20East%20Coast%2C%20and%20it%20features%20dual%20seats%20on%20each%20side%20%E2%80%94%20perfect%20for%20couples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWalking%20through%20the%20cabin%2C%20I%20appreciated%20the%20light%20blue%20color%20scheme%20and%20the%20fun%20flight%20attendant%20uniforms.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221991%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20flight%20attendant%20onboard%20Hawaiian%20with%20a%20flower-themed%20uniform.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564f837fd6200867dcfda50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221493%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20flight%20attendant%20onboard%20Hawaiian%20during%20the%20return%20flight.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHawaiian%20is%20a%20leisure-focused%20carrier%2C%20and%20I%20liked%20its%20laid-back%20ambiance.%20The%20landmarks%20and%20culture%20of%20Hawaii%20even%20inspired%20the%20inflight%20safety%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%2C%20the%20plane%20did%20lack%20WiFi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20soon%20made%20it%20to%20seats%2042J%20and%2042H.%20I%20chose%20this%20particular%20section%20because%20of%20the%20bigger%20aisle%20in%20the%2