ubtedly%2C%20on%20this%20occasion%20the%20scenario%20should%20be%20that%20the%20support%20for%20any%20party%20be%20based%20on%20consensus.%20Or%2C%20at%20least%20a%20decision%20should%20be%20based%20on%20the%20view%20of%20the%20large%20majority.%20But%20taking%20into%20consideration%20the%20ground%20realities%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20is%20divided.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20delicate%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20further%20underscores%20the%20need%20to%20stop%20Muslim%20votes%20from%20being%20divided%2C%20and%20points%20out%20that%20it%20is%20on%20account%20of%20this%20possibility%20that%20the%20panel%20decided%20not%20to%20support%20any%20political%20party.%20Instead%2C%20it%20requested%20the%20members%20of%20the%20community%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20candidate%20who%20has%20secular%20credentials%2C%20one%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20is%20less%20harmful%20for%20the%20community%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20fact%20that%20Maulana%20Khalid%20is%20the%20fifth%20president%20of%20the%20AIMPLB%2C%20he%20continues%20to%20remain%20an%20influential%20figure.%20Though%20a%20non-political%20figure%2C%20he%20enjoys%20the%20support%20of%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(MIM)%20president%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20who%20in%20July%20this%20year%2C%20led%20a%20delegation%20of%20clerics%2C%20including%20Maulana%20Khalid%2C%20to%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20camp%20office%20in%20Pragathi%20Bhavan%20to%20urge%20him%20to%20not%20support%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20yet%20another%20example%2C%20the%20Jamaat-e-Islami%E2%80%99s%20Telangana%20chapter%20refrained%20from%20announcing%20their%20support%20to%20either%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20BRS.%20Instead%2C%20its%20political%20committee%20chose%20to%20support%20individual%20candidates%20contesting%20the%20119%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20Telangana.%20Unlike%20their%20previous%20stance%2C%20the%20Jamaat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Ftelangana-assembly%2Fjamaat-e-islami-telangana-supports-69-congress-41-brs-candidates%2Farticle67561775.ece%5C%22%3Echose%20to%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%2070%20Congress%20candidates%2C%2040%20BRS%20candidates%2C%20and%20seven%20AIMIM%20candidates.%20This%20is%20a%20change%20in%20its%20approach.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20Jamaat%20supported%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20in%202018%2C%20after%20extensive%20deliberations%20and%20sharing%20concerns%20with%20the%20top%20party%20leadership%2C%20announced%20its%20support%20to%20the%20BRS%20%5Bthen%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20meetings%20which%20led%20to%20the%20announcement%2C%20there%20were%20internal%20differences%20between%20political%20committee%20members.%20Some%20wanted%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20openly%20support%20the%20BRS.%20But%20others%20felt%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20changing%2C%20and%20that%20the%20inroads%20Congress%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20making%20must%20not%20be%20ignored.%20Eventually%2C%20extensive%20consultations%20and%20ground%20surveys%20were%20done.%20They%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20a%20non-partisan%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Jamaat%20member%20closely%20following%20the%20developments%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20yet%20another%20example%2C%20Jamiat-i-Ulama%E2%80%99s%20two%20factions%20ended%20up%20throwing%20their%20weight%20behind%20the%20two%20contenders.%20While%20the%20Jamiat%E2%80%99s%20Maulana%20Arshad%20Madani%20faction%2C%20with%20its%20headquarters%20in%20Yakutpura%20in%20the%20Old%20City%2C%20endorsed%20the%20BRS%2C%20the%20Maulana%20Mahmood%20Madani%20faction%2C%20which%20operates%20from%20Amberpet%E2%80%99s%20Zam%20Zam%20Masjid%2C%20supported%20the%20Congress.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20latter%20was%20busy%20extensively%20touring%20many%20of%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%2033%20districts%20to%20question%20CM%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20treatment%20of%20Muslims%2C%20especially%20those%20residing%20in%20districts%20other%20than%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fresurgent-congress-telangana-brs%5C%22%3ECan%20the%20Resurgent%20Congress%20Wrest%20Telangana%20from%20the%20BRS%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%20constitute%20over%2050%20lakh%20of%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20population.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20official%20figures%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Muslim%20voters%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%2040%20lakh.%20According%20to%20the%202011%20census%2C%20the%20concentration%20of%20Muslims%20is%20highest%20in%20composite%20districts%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20Ranga%20Reddy%20and%20Nizamabad.%20Members%20of%20political%20parties%20believe%20that%20there%20are%20around%2030%20assembly%20constituencies%20where%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20sentiment%20is%20palpable.%20A%20section%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20appears%20to%20be%20disenchanted%20with%20the%20BRS.%20For%20their%20part%2C%20the%20pink%20party%20did%20make%20impressive%20budgetary%20allocations%2C%20with%20a%20significant%20portion%20going%20to%20the%20over%20200%20minority%20residential%20schools%2C%20and%20other%20minority%20welfare%20schemes.%20During%20its%20tenure%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20once%20a%20riot-prone%20city%2C%20did%20not%20see%20any%20major%20communal%20clash.%20Several%20Muslims%20themselves%20have%20admitted%20that%20Telangana%20and%20Hyderabad%20are%20relatively%20much%20safer%20compared%20to%20states%20in%20North%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKCR%20has%20backed%20many%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20policies%2C%20including%20demonetisation%20and%20GST.%20The%20promised%2012%25%20reservations%20for%20Muslims%20has%20not%20materialised.%20But%20more%20importantly%2C%20there%20is%20a%20persistent%20perception%20among%20many%20Muslims%20that%20KCR%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bjp-brs-and-the-truth-behind-the-conspiracy-theories%5C%22%3Esecret%20understanding%20with%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20perception%20is%20unlikely%20to%20fade.%20Many%20are%20talking%20in%20such%20terms%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohammed%20Faiz%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%20small%20businessman%20from%20Malakpet%2C%20an%20AIMIM%20stronghold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20believe%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20remove%20the%20BJP%20from%20power%20is%20to%20support%20the%20Congress.%20This%20is%20likely%20because%20parliamentary%20elections%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20mid-next%20year%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20Given%20the%20differing%20opinions%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20the%20Muslim%20community%20will%20vote.%20The%20answer%20will%20be%20clear%20only%20on%20December%203%2C%20when%20votes%20will%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701164744000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F28145637%2F33877013268_16c99d849f_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-poll-date-parties-sights-muslim-voters%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20opinion%20of%20Muslims%20continues%20to%20be%20divided.%20To%20vote%20for%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20or%20the%20Congress%20party%20remains%20a%20key%20question.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-poll-date-parties-sights-muslim-voters%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jong%20Ho%20to%20say%20'I%20Do'%20with%20non-celebrity%20sweetheart%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701164618000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105559957%2Cimgsize-279450.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indi