Third-generation%20idol%20Hwang%20Hyun%20Jin%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Yigyer%2C%20is%20getting%20married%20on%20December%2023.%20She%20shared%20the%20exciting%20news%20through%20an%20Instagram%20post%2C%20revealing%20her%20soon-to-be%20husband's%20good%20looks.%20With%20only%20100%20days%20left%20until%20the%20big%20day%2C%20Hwang%20Hyun%20Jin%20expressed%20her%20astonishment%20at%20how%20fast%20time%20was%20flying.%20Beyond%20her%20entertainment%20career%2C%20she%20is%20recognized%20as%20the%20daughter%20of%20Korean%20football%20hero%20Hwang%20Sun%20Hong%2C%20who%20led%20Korea's%202002%20World%20Cup%20team%20to%20a%20remarkable%20fourth-place%20finish.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fthird-generation-idol-yigyer-shares-excitement-for-december-wedding%2Farticleshow%2F105559850.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKeep%20Bags%20Ready%26quot%3B%3A%20Workers'%20Families%20Told%20As%20Tunnel%20Op%20In%20Final%20Stretch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20relatives%20of%20the%2041%20workers%20trapped%20in%20a%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20prepared%26quot%3B%20as%20rescuers%20said%20they%20have%20cleared%20the%20final%20few%20meters%20of%20debris.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKeep%20their%20clothes%20and%20bags%20ready%2C%26quot%3B%20officials%20told%20the%20families%20who%20have%20been%20keeping%20a%20vigil%20outside%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20workers%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Uttarkashi%20after%20being%20rescued%20where%20a%20special%20ward%20with%2041%20beds%20has%20been%20set%20up%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnxious%20families%20are%20hoping%20to%20see%20their%20loved%20ones%20soon%20as%20the%20rescue%20operation%20is%20over.%20%26quot%3BOne%20family%20member%20will%20be%20accompanying%20each%20worker%20in%20the%20ambulance%20while%20they%20are%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20skilled%20team%20of%20workers%20started%20the%20manual%20drilling%20of%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20yesterday%20after%20parts%20of%20the%20broken%20drill%20were%20removed%20from%20the%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManual%20drilling%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20%26quot%3Brat%20miners%26quot%3B-%20labourers%20used%20to%20drilling%20narrow%20shafts%20as%20part%20of%20a%20primitive%20method%20of%20coal%20extraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20rescue%20operations%20were%20earlier%20suspended%20for%20three%20days%20when%20a%20US-made%20auger%20machine%20deployed%20to%20drill%20and%20push%20in%20pipes%20through%20the%20rubble%20to%20prepare%20an%20escape%20passage%20for%20the%20workers%20developed%20a%20snag%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManual%20drilling%20is%20a%20slow%20and%20labour-intensive%20process%20in%20which%20the%20rat-hole%20miners%20go%20through%20the%20huge%20pipe%2C%20drill%20manually%20and%20bring%20out%20the%20debris%20by%20shovels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20going%20through%20the%20pipes%20would%20be%20difficult%20for%20them%2C%20an%20official%20said%20that%20the%20workers%20will%20be%20provided%20with%20a%20helmet%2C%20a%20uniform%2C%20mask%20and%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%2C%20repeated%20attempts%20to%20rescue%20the%20workers%20have%20failed%20because%20of%20challenges%20including%20the%20topography%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20rocks%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20workers%20are%20mentally%20stable%20and%20physically%20fit%20despite%20being%20trapped%20for%20over%20two%20weeks.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20adequately%20clothed%20and%20when%20we%20speak%20to%20them%2C%20they%20say%20they%20will%20walk%20out%20on%20their%20own.%20That's%20the%20kind%20of%20mental%20strength%20they%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%