3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Indian%20Railways%20Performance%20Highlight%20report%20has%20noted%20that%20the%20railways%20has%20not%20commissioned%20any%20new%20lines%20with%20its%20safety%20system%20Kavach%20till%20October%20this%20year.%20In%20the%20April%E2%80%93October%20period%20last%20year%2C%2010%20km%20of%20such%20lines%20were%20commissioned%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Flogistics%2Fno-new-kavach-lines-commissioned-till-oct-31-railways-performance-report%2Farticle67579827.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2527Commissioning%2520of%2520Kavach%2520is%2520Nil%2Ckm%2520till%2520Oct%252031%252C%25202023%2527%26amp%3Btext%3DIndian%2520Railways%2520has%2520not%2520commissioned%2Cyear%252C%2520the%2520performance%2520report%2520mentions.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20Business%20Line%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommissioning%20of%20Kavach%20is%20Nil%20till%20October%2031%2C%20compare(d)%20to%2010%20km%20last%20fiscal%20during%20same%20period%20and%20against%20the%20target%20of%20637%20km%20till%20Oct%2031%2C%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20performance%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKavach%20is%20an%20Automatic%20Train%20Protection%20(ATP)%20system%20created%20by%20the%20Research%20Design%20and%20Standards%20Organisation%20(RDSO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20no%20lines%20under%20Kavach%20were%20commissioned%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20new%20line%20setting%20up%20was%20186.65%20km%2C%20the%20doubling%20of%20lines%20was%201019.69%20km%2C%20and%20gauge%20conversion%20(from%20narrow%20to%20broad%20gauge)%20was%2096%20km.%20A%20cumulative%20of%201302.34%20km%20was%20covered%20till%20Oct-end%2C%20at%20least%2025%20per%20cent-odd%20lesser%20than%20last%20year%20(across%20these%20categories)%20which%20covered%201728.55%20km%20(%20that%20included%20new%20line%20laying%20of%2052.8%20kms%2C%20gauge%20conversion%20across%20102%20km%2C%20and%20double%20lining%3A%201573.75%20km)%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20cause%20of%20concern%20in%20view%20of%20additional%20expenditure%20on%20this%20account%20during%20the%20same%20period%20and%20less%20commissioning%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20railways%E2%80%99%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findian-railways-sharp-rise-train-accidents-2022%5C%22%3Ealso%20noted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20was%20an%20increase%20in%20consequential%20accidents%20across%20the%20Indian%20Railways%E2%80%99%20network%20in%202021-22%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%20According%20to%20official%20data%2C%20nine%20were%20killed%20in%20train%20accidents%20in%202021-22%20and%2045%20were%20injured.%20No%20loss%20of%20life%20or%20injuries%20were%20reported%20in%202020-21.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701163858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F28145254%2F13286908034_bb8f865649_h.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findian-railways-hasnt-commissioned-new-kavach-lines-this-year-performance-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CCommissioning%20of%20Kavach%20is%20Nil%20till%20October%2031%2C%20compare(d)%20to%2010%20km%20last%20fiscal%20during%20same%20period%20and%20against%20the%20target%20of%20637%20km%20till%20Oct%2031%2C%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20performance%20report%20noted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findian-railways-hasnt-commissioned-new-kavach-lines-this-year-performance-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Park%20Hyung%20opens%20up%20about%20BTS%20V's%20military%20service%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701163790000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105559500%2Cimgsize-821828.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fe