0to%20pay%20elsewhere...%20if%20required%2C%20we%20will%20deal%20with%20it.%20But%20here%20the%20limited%20point%20is%20whether%20our%20order%20has%20been%20complied%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kaul%20underlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20had%20expressed%20its%20inability%20to%20contribute%20the%20required%20funds%2C%20after%20which%20the%20court%20sought%20a%20record%20of%20funds%20spent%20by%20the%20ruling%20AAP%20on%20ads%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2024%2C%20top%20court%20noted%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20which%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-directs-delhi-to-pay-rs-500-crore-for-rapid-rail-to-meerut-3968265%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20to%20contribute%20Rs%20500%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20this%20project%2C%20had%20spent%20more%20than%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20on%20ads%20in%20the%20last%20three%20financial%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20had%20been%20told%20to%20provide%20Rs%20415%20crore%20within%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20Delhi%20government%20counsel%20assured%20the%20court%20full%20payments%20will%20be%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RRTS%20project%20-%20an%2082-km%20stretch%20costing%20nearly%20Rs%2032%2C000%20crore%20-%20entails%20semi-high%20speed%20rail%20corridors%20connecting%20Delhi%20to%20Alwar%2C%20Panipat%2C%20and%20Meerut.%20Around%2013%20km%20is%20within%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20managed%20by%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20Transport%20Corporation%20-%20a%20centre-states%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%