20central%20government%20to%20impose%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20companies%2C%20firms%20and%20associations%20from%20employing%20or%20soliciting%20any%20work%20or%20performance%2C%20taking%20of%20any%20services%2C%20or%20entering%20into%20any%20association%20and%20so%20on%20with%20any%20Pakistani%20artiste%2C%20including%20its%20cine%20workers%2C%20singers%2C%20musicians%2C%20lyricists%20and%20technicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20had%20dismissed%20the%20petition%2C%20saying%20the%20reliefs%20it%20seeks%20is%20a%20retrograde%20step%20in%20promoting%20cultural%20harmony%2C%20unity%20and%20peace%2C%20and%20has%20no%20merit%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20must%20understand%20that%20in%20order%20to%20be%20a%20patriot%2C%20one%20need%20not%20be%20inimical%20to%20those%20from%20abroad%20especially%2C%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20true%20patriot%20is%20a%20person%20who%20is%20selfless%2C%20who%20is%20devoted%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20his%20country%2C%20which%20he%20cannot%20be%20unless%20he%20is%20a%20person%20who%20is%20good%20at%20heart.%20A%20person%20who%20is%20good%20at%20heart%20would%20welcome%20in%20his%20country%20any%20activity%20which%20promotes%20peace%2C%20harmony%2C%20and%20tranquillity%20within%20the%20country%20and%20across%20the%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArts%2C%20music%2C%20sports%2C%20culture%2C%20dance%20and%20so%20on%20are%20the%20activities%20which%20rise%20above%20nationalities%2C%20cultures%20and%20nations%2C%20and%20truly%20bring%20about%20peace%2C%20tranquillity%2C%20unity%20and%20harmony%20in%20nation%20and%20between%20nations%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20said%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20noted%20that%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20Pakistan%20was%20a%20participant.%20This%20happened%20only%20because%20of%20appreciable%20positive%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20overall%20peace%20and%20harmony%20in%20consonance%20with%20Article%2051%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20which%20is%20about%20promotion%20of%20international%20peace%20and%20security%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701158160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fe8bgk2vo_supreme-court-getty_625x300_31_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-be-so-narrow-minded-supreme-court-on-plea-to-ban-pak-artists-in-india-4612982%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20dismissed%20a%20plea%20seeking%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20artistes%20from%20Pakistan%20to%20perform%20or%20work%20in%20India%2C%20and%20asked%20the%20petitioner%20not%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bso%20narrow-minded%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-be-so-narrow-minded-supreme-court-on-plea-to-ban-pak-artists-in-india-4612982%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-be-so-narrow-minded-supreme-court-on-plea-to-ban-pak-artists-in-india-4612982%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-be-so-narrow-minded-supreme-court-on-plea-to-ban-pak-artists-in-india-4612982%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Overworked%20Chinese%20Student%20Dies%20Live-Streaming%20Gaming%20Sessions%20For%205%20Days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20media%20company%20in%20central%20China%20has%20refuted%20allegations%20of%20responsibility%20for%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20a%20college%20student.%20The%20student%2C%20identified%20as%20Li%20Hao%2C%20died%20after%20participating%20in%20five%20consecutive%20all-night%20live-streaming%20sessions%20for%20the%20company%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThePaper.cn%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELi%20Hao%20was%20in%20his%20final%20year%20at%20Henan's%20Pingdingshan%20Vocational%20and%20Technical%20College%2C%20fulfilling%20an%20internship%20requirement%20to%20meet%20curriculum%20obligations%20before%20his%20anticipated%20graduation%20in%20June%20of%20the%20following%20year.%20His%20role%20involved%20serving%20as%20an%20online%20game%20streamer%20for%20Henan%20Qinyi%20Culture%20and%20Media%20Co.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unfortunate%20incident%20occurred%20on%20November%2010%20in%20Li's%20rented%20house%20in%20Zhengzhou%2C%20Henan%20province.%20Roommates%20discovered%20him%20breathing%20rapidly%20and%20unresponsive%20during%20sleep%2C%20prompting%20them%20to%20seek%20emergency%20assistance.%20Despite%20their%20efforts%2C%20Li%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20upon%20arrival%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bcooperation%20agreement%26quot%3B%20obtained%20by%20the%20newspaper%2C%20Li%20was%20obligated%20to%20livestream%20for%20240%20hours%20in%2026%20days%20and%20upload%2015%20short%20videos%20each%20month%20to%20earn%20a%20minimum%20salary%20of%203%2C000%20yuan.%20Li%20had%20worked%20the%20day%20shift%20since%20October%20but%20transitioned%20to%20the%20night%20shift%20on%20November%205%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fa%2F202311%2F20%2FWS655b34e7a31090682a5ef228.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EChina%20Daily%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20engaged%20in%20live-streaming%20sessions%20from%209%20pm%20to%206%20am%20for%20five%20consecutive%20nights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecords%20indicate%20that%20Li%20conducted%2089%20live-streaming%20sessions%20between%20October%2015%20and%20November%2010%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3242427%2Fgames-death-online-anger-family-china-student-who-died-after-marathon-live-stream-gaming-sessions%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELi's%20father%20revealed%20that%20the%20company%20requested%20the%20shift%20change%20due%20to%20better%20tips%20and%20higher%20earnings.%20However%2C%20Li%20was%20reportedly%20unhappy%20with%20the%20new%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20represented%20legally%20by%20Zhang%2C%20denied%20all%20responsibility%2C%20emphasizing%20a%20cooperative%20agreement%20with%20Li.%20%26quot%3BWe%20provide%20a%20venue%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhang%20stated%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20only%20take%20a%20commission%20from%20viewer%20gifts%20given%20to%20the%20live-streamer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhang%20acknowledged%20the%20challenges%20many%20live-streamers%20face%20in%20managing%20the%20extent%20of%20their%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20compensation%2C%20the%20employer%20has%20offered%205%2C000%20yuan%20or%20Rs%2058%2C750%20to%20Li's%20family.%20However%2C%20the%20company%20is%20now%20facing%20public%20outrage%20on%20Chinese%20social%20media%20for%20its%20perceived%20irresponsible%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701157980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fp323p768_online-gaming-_625x300_28_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Foverworked-chinese-student-dies-live-streaming-gaming-sessions-for-5-days-4613058%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unfortunate%20incident%20occurred%20on%20November%2010%20in%20Li's%20rented%20house%20in%20Zhengzhou%2C%20Henan%20province.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Foverworked-chinese-student-dies-live-streaming-gaming-sessions-for-5-days-4613058%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Foverworked-