d-rides-in-on-bike-shoots-man-dead%2Farticleshow%2F105554667.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'The%20Liver%20Doc'%20Dr%20Abby%20Philips%20Lodges%20Complaint%20Against%20Right-Winger%20for%20Online%20Abuse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F07150301%2FScreenshot-2023-10-07-at-3.02.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Cyriac%20Abby%20Philips%2C%20a%20hepatologist%20widely%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98theliverdoc%E2%80%99%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20a%20right-wing%20sympathiser%2C%20Vijay%20Patel%20alleging%20online%20verbal%20abuse%2C%20harassment%20and%20vulgarity.%20The%20complaint%20was%20filed%20at%20the%20Palarivattom%20police%20station%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20was%20also%20sent%20to%20the%20Kochi%20Commissioner%20of%20Police.%20The%20Commissioner%20has%20forwarded%20the%20complaint%20to%20the%20Ernakulam%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20for%20thorough%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Abby%2C%20renowned%20for%20sharing%20medical%20research%20and%20educational%20content%20on%20his%20social%20media%20account%20%E2%80%98theliverdoc%E2%80%99%2C%20took%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20November%2023%2C%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20alleged%20incident.%20%E2%80%9CLast%20night%20until%20early%20morning%20hours%2C%20I%20was%20subjected%20to%20terrible%20and%20vulgar%20online%20abuse%2C%20harassment%2C%20vulgarity%2C%20and%20character%20assassination%20initiated%20by%20a%20Hindutva%20handle%20operated%20by%20a%20man%2C%20Mr%20Vijay%20Patel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbby%20said%20that%20the%20confrontation%20began%20when%20he%20spoke%20about%20the%20Ayurveda%20group%20Patanjali%20and%20its%20leader%20Baba%20Ramdev.%20He%20alleged%20that%20Vijay%20Patel%20responded%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20scientifically%20or%20rationally%2C%20but%20using%20communalism%20and%20hurling%20religious%20slurs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Patel%20tweeted%20calling%20Abby%20a%20%E2%80%98propaganda%20doctor%E2%80%99%20who%20always%20targets%20Ayurveda%20and%20Yoga%20%E2%80%98because%20he%20belongs%20to%20the%20missionary%20cartel%20which%20uses%20the%20modern%20medical%20field%20as%20their%20conversion%20factory%E2%80%99.%20Vijay%20Patel%20then%20asked%20people%20if%20they%20want%20to%20know%20Abby%20and%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Vijay%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20Dr%20Abby%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmassive%20right-wing%20Hindu%20nationalist%20social%20media%20abusive%20machinery%E2%80%9D%20targeted%20him%2C%20inundating%20his%20posts%20with%20abuse%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20vulgar%20comments.%20He%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20posted%20on%20matters%20of%20medical%20science%20and%20medical%20education%20simplified%20for%20the%20people.%20It%20is%20my%20passion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20having%20taken%20the%20legal%20action%2C%20he%20expressed%20his%20faith%20in%20the%20Kerala%20Police%20Department%2C%20the%20Kochi%20City%20Police%2C%20and%20the%20State%20Cyber%20Cell.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20faith%20that%20they%20will%20hunt%20this%20man%20down%20and%20bring%20him%20what%20he%20deserves.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Abby%20Philips%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20controversy%2C%20having%20received%20approximately%2015%20legal%20notices%20over%20the%20years.%20He%20is%20known%20for%20his%20critical%20comments%20about%20how%20improperly%20prepared%20AYUSH%20remedies%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20liver%20health.%20He%20got%20a%20notice%20from%20the%20Kerala%20State%20Medical%20Council%20for%20Indian%20Systems%20of%20Medicine%20for%20an%20interview%20regarding%20the%20ill%20effects%20of%20ingesting%20a%20widely%20used%20herb%20Giloy%20(Tinospora%20cordifolia)%2C%20the%20charges%20of%20which%20were%20later%20dropped.%20He%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20research%20team%20that%20published%20a%20study%20that%20found%20that%20homoeopathic%20remedies%20could%20promote%20severe%20liver%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fkerala%2Fdr-abby-thelieverdoc-lodges-complaint-against-right-winger-vijay-patel-for-online-abuse%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20News%20Minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701154841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F07150301%2FScreenshot-2023-10-07-at-3.02.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-liver-doc-dr-abby-philips-lodges-complaint-against-right-winger-for-online-abuse%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Abby%20said%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20right-wing%20Hindu%20nationalist%20social%20media%20abusive%20machinery%26quot%3B%20targeted%20him%2C%20inundating%20his%20posts%20with%20abuse%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20vulgar%20comments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-liver-doc-dr-abby-philips-lodges-complaint-against-right-winger-for-online-abuse%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Suffocating'%3A%20Israeli%20hostages%20speak%20of%20food%20shortages%20and%20darkness%20in%20Hamas%20captivity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701154260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-israel-hostage-hamas_6372242.jpg%3F20231125174948%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisraeli-hostages-speak-of-food-shortages-and-darkness-in-hamas