tics%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RTI%20also%20showed%20that%20three%20out%20of%20eight%20member%20posts%20are%20vacant.%20In%20March%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Lokpal%20was%20criticised%20by%20a%20parliamentary%20committee%20for%20its%20non-performance%20and%20failure%20to%20fill%20the%20post%20of%20chairperson%20and%20other%20members%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fnov%2F28%2Fheadless-lokpal-wakes-up-to-deal-with-the-moitra-case-2636807.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMoreover%252C%2520three%2520out%2520of%2520eight%2Cresponse%2520on%2520microblogging%2520platform%2520X.timesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fngos-stoking-ethnic-tension-in-manipur-says-sc-panel%2Farticleshow%2F105542010.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20had%20approached%20the%20Lokpal%20on%20October%2021%20alleging%20that%20Moitra%20had%20compromised%20national%20security%20by%20sharing%20her%20parliament%20login%20credentials%20with%20unauthorised%20persons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Hope%20Rs%2013%2C000%20crore%20Adani%20coal%20scam%20merits%20CBI%20PE%20before%20my%20witchhunt%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahua%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Famused-to-see-how-headless-lokpal-with-no-full-time-chairman-referred-my-case-to-cbi-mahua-moitra%2Fcid%2F1982649%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELokpal%E2%80%99s%20efficacy%20in%20question%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20parliamentary%20panel%20on%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20headed%20by%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20said%20the%20body%20has%20not%20prosecuted%20a%20single%20person%20accused%20of%20corruption%20to%20date%20and%20its%20performance%20seems%20to%20be%20far%20from%20satisfactory%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Lokpal%20Act%20was%20passed%20in%202013%2C%20the%20first%20Lokpal%20was%20appointed%20in%202019%20with%20eight%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20panel%2C%20only%20three%20complaints%20were%20fully%20investigated%20and%20nearly%2090%25%20of%20the%20complaints%20were%20disposed%20of.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20anti-corruption%20body%20is%20also%20required%20to%20have%20a%20prosecution%20wing%20and%20an%20inquiry%20wing%20to%20prosecute%20guilty%20public%20servants%20but%20both%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20constituted.%20The%20body%20has%2032%20members%20against%20the%20sanctioned%20strength%20of%2082.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701152940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F26174104%2FMahua-Mitra.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahua-moitra-calls-lokpal-headless-points-to-rti-showing-nearly-half-the-member-posts-vacant%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20March%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Lokpal%20was%20criticised%20by%20a%20parliamentary%20committee%20for%20its%20non-performance%20and%20failure%20to%20fill%20the%20post%20of%20chairperson%20and%20other%20members.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahua-moitra-calls-lokpal-headless-points-to-rti-showing-nearly-half-the-member-posts-vacant%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TikTok%20Owner%20Bytedance%20Poised%20to%20Close%20%E2%80%98Marvel%20Snap%E2%80%99%20Game%20Publisher%20Nuverse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701152097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%