%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECeline%20Halioua%20founded%20a%20biotech%20startup%20developing%20drugs%20to%20extend%20dog%20lifespans.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Loyal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELoyal%20for%20Dogs%20is%20developing%20drugs%20to%20extend%20doggie%20lifespans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20drug%20just%20cleared%20a%20key%20FDA%20hurdle%2C%20a%20sign%20the%20agency%20is%20ready%20to%20take%20longevity%20seriously.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20injection%20could%20be%20available%20in%20veterinary%20offices%20by%202026.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20anti-aging%20drug%20for%20dogs%20is%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20doctor's%20offices%2C%20after%20it%20cleared%20a%20key%20regulatory%20hurdle%20with%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FDA)%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Floyalfordogs.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELoyal%20for%20Dogs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20that%20its%20first-of-its-kind%20longevity%20drug%20received%20the%20first%20of%20three%20green%20lights%20needed%20for%20FDA%20approval.%20The%20decision%2C%20made%20in%20early%20November%2C%20is%20essentially%20a%20vote%20of%20confidence%20from%20federal%20regulators%20that%20this%20drug%20should%20actually%20work%20to%20extend%20dogs'%20lifespans%2C%20based%20on%20evidence%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoyal's%20new%20drug%2C%20called%20LOY-001%20is%20an%20injection%20that%20dogs%20over%207%20years%20and%2040%20pounds%20could%20receive%20at%20their%20veterinarian's%20office%20roughly%20every%20three%20to%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%3F%20Add%20more%20years%20of%20healthy%20living%20onto%20the%20pets'%20lives%2C%20at%20a%20relatively%20reasonable%20price%20of%20%26quot%3Bmid%20double%20digits%26quot%3B%20a%20month%2C%20Loyal%20CEO%20and%20founder%20Celine%20Halioua%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Halioua%20expects%20the%20drug%2